						               													<description>Hellapoliisi is a delicious game of cards, which is based on the super-popular Finnish police cooker recipe site. The raw materials generated by the blog writer? In this delicious game of card players, the task is to combine the right material with the right recipe. Challenge other players, no doubt their knowledge of food and recipe cards to steal from their hands! The player who collects the most cards in a recipe, wins the game! Enjoy a delicious dinner with your friends!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game has large cards (foods) and small cards (components). Each large card back has a recipe. On each turn, players draws 8 cards cards and takes one food card from the below of the deck. Then the hourglass is turned and players now has to place all components that fit to that food. Trick is that even a 1 wrong one will nullify a score, so be careful. Each correct one with no wrong cards lets you keep the food with cards. At the end of the game you read all the cards you have placed on top of your foods. You get 10 extra points when you have places all components named at the back of the card.&amp;#10;Winner is the game with the most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
